cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.CL, cs.MM, cs.IR 

Reasoning: 
- cs.CV (Computer Vision) is the most likely category as the paper deals with visual features and compatibility prediction in fashion datasets. 
- cs.LG (Machine Learning) is also likely as the paper proposes a graph neural network model for learning product embeddings. 
- cs.CL (Computation and Language) is another possibility as the paper deals with natural language tasks such as fill in the blank. 
- cs.MM (Multimedia) is a possible category as the paper deals with fashion datasets that include images and text. 
- cs.IR (Information Retrieval) is also a possibility as the paper deals with predicting compatibility between clothing items based on their features and context.
